 Messenger of Allah has written for me.\u201d I\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25346,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/28\/dua-refuge-bad-character\/","url_meta":{"origin":15494,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: I seek refuge in Allah from bad character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 28, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Qutbah ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in you from evil character traits, evil deeds, and evil desires.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3591 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u0642\u0637\u0628\u0629 \u0628\u0646 \u0645\u0627\u0644\u0643 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34519,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/10\/25\/jibreel-teaches-prophet-refuge\/","url_meta":{"origin":15494,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Refuge: Gabriel teaches the Prophet to seek refuge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 25, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdur Rahman ibn Khanbash reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGabriel came to me and he said: O Muhammad, speak! I said: What should I say? Gabriel said: Say, I seek refuge in the p